name: Central: A Look Back and a Look Forward by Wicked Good Development
summary: If you utilize Java or any other JVM, there’s a good chance you know the Maven Central repository. Today’s episode brings long-time maintainers and contributors of Maven Central, Brian Fox, Jason Swank, and Joel Orlina to the mic to rehash the early days of Maven Central, lessons learned from managing open source ecosystems, and bring insight into the platform’s practical software supply chain management capabilities of the past, present, and future.
